{"id":509835,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":4,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"纪念“五一”国际劳动节","genre":"","count":"250","ytitle":"","mtitle":"学大庆掀高潮","ftitle":"","authors":["龚咏燕"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沪东纺织机械厂　龚咏燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开大步去加油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首挺胸雄赳赳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我摸一下布机轻声唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是祖国的翻身油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻一闻呀扑鼻香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们对它情最厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一眼呀闪闪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆景象眼里收——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏草原头顶天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“两论”光辉暖心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命创业不怕苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁人精神遍神州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中筑起大庆路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗指引去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学大庆，金鼓送来决心书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀热潮，银锣催咱快加油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新一辈，猛攻猛打争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老一辈，群策群力献智谋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧锣密鼓声追声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点兵点将数风流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纬线——横穿塞北风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经线——直上重霄九，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望一幅画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿!咱为共产主义织彩楼。"}]}